three main constitutions

00:02:31.540 --> 00:02:33.370 align:middle line:90%
that are described.

00:02:33.370 --> 00:02:36.520 align:middle line:84%
It is called the vata,
the pitta, and the kapha.

00:02:36.520 --> 00:02:39.070 align:middle line:84%
