air, aether, and Earth.

00:02:49.870 --> 00:02:55.540 align:middle line:84%
Every atom and matter also has
all of those five elements.

00:02:55.540 --> 00:03:00.940 align:middle line:84%
In our body, every cell is
made up of those five elements.

00:03:00.940 --> 00:03:05.290 align:middle line:84%
