different from the nature

00:03:05.290 --> 00:03:08.710 align:middle line:84%
and the whole
universal existence.

00:03:08.710 --> 00:03:12.040 align:middle line:90%
We are part of the whole.

00:03:12.040 --> 00:03:15.220 align:middle line:84%
