unique constitution--

00:03:15.220 --> 00:03:19.090 align:middle line:84%
depending on our
genetic makeup, you

00:03:19.090 --> 00:03:23.290 align:middle line:84%
could have either just a
dominant vata constitution

00:03:23.290 --> 00:03:26.230 align:middle line:84%
or a pitta constitution,
or a kapha constitution.

00:03:26.230 --> 00:03:29.770 align:middle line:84%
Or you could have a combination
of vata-pitta, pitta-kapha,

00:03:29.770 --> 00:03:32.050 align:middle line:90%
or the kapha-vata constitution.

00:03:32.050 --> 00:03:36.910 align:middle line:84%
The vata constitution has the
air and the aether element

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:37.960 align:middle line:90%
dominant.

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:41.350 align:middle line:84%
The pitta constitution has
the fire and the water element

00:03:41.350 --> 00:03:42.760 align:middle line:90%
dominant in it.

00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:45.310 align:middle line:84%
