constitution has the water

00:03:45.310 --> 00:03:47.140 align:middle line:90%
and the Earth element dominant.

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:49.340 align:middle line:84%
We do have all
five constitutions,

00:03:49.340 --> 00:03:50.870 align:middle line:90%
but these are the dominant ones.

00:03:50.870 --> 00:03:54.670 align:middle line:84%
And we are defined by the
dominant constitution.

00:03:54.670 --> 00:03:56.800 align:middle line:84%
Depending on our
dominant constitution,

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:59.620 align:middle line:84%
